The unity project is uploaded here.  The instructions for the current functions of the inventory system are displayed when interacting with it.  Here are the controls again:
- 1: Select blue item
- 2: Select green item
- 3: Select yellow item
- 4: Select red item
- S: Sell highlighted item from inventory
- Right Click: Rotate current item
- Left Click: Place current item in inventory (If it fits and you have enough currency)
